(5947, 7323, 'Years (2013)', '作曲：Mister Mouth (嘴哥樂團)\n\nNow I realize we can never tell either right or wrong,\nAnd I know it''s because we''ve never met each other before.\n\nFrom now on, I won''t go anywhere but here to stay\nFor that day while everybody is coming back.\n\nI will always be right here\nCause we are just the same.\nThe sound will bring us back to this place.\nNo matter who came or left\nAt this time we have all night.\n\nNow I realize we can never tell either right or wrong,\nAnd I know it''s because we''ve never met each other before.\nNow I realize we can never tell either right or wrong,\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ Mojim.com　魔鏡歌詞網 \nBut at this time we have all night\nTo sing the song, It''s all for you.\n\nFrom now on, I won''t go anywhere but here to stay\nFor that day while everybody is coming back.\n\nI will always be right here\nCause we are just the same.\nThe sound will bring us back to this place.\nNo matter who came or left\nAt this time everybody is coming back.\n\nSo many years have gone.\nSo many years will come.\nSo many years\n', '2013-02-08 00:00:00', 0, 4, 5, '', 'Scarecrow', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-07-08 15:03:40', '2015-02-16 15:48:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5948, 127427, 'StreetVoice夏季選集', '從2011年底首發的《冬季選集》，我們展開了一趟新的旅程。\n \n在Urban Folk的風景裡，我們曾經簡單開心地微笑，直到發現周圍環境逐漸轉變，\n以為穩定的鬆動了，認定正確的顛反了，聽來和諧的走音了，\n我們企圖踩穩腳步，仍有地動天搖之感。\n \n音樂當然可以提供躲避的溫柔鄉，但那不是我們生活在這塊土地上的意義。    \n所以呼喚著夥伴們一起勇敢推開昔日的安全感，再次摸索上路。\n \n嬉皮是不存在的鄉愁，於是我們想像並重塑這個世代的自由，為它奔放起來。\n是的，過程中當然要流汗，熱呼呼的身體，才能與那些緊密交織的器樂充分回應，產生前進的力量。\n \n隨時隨地都可以是廣闊草原上的夏天，只要你握住了這一切。', '2012-08-18 00:00:00', 0, 3, 5, '蔡坤奇(奇哥)', 'StreetVoice', 0, '887375000022', 1, 0, '2013-07-08 18:02:01', '2015-02-16 15:48:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
